;;; Commentary:

;; More friendly interface (display transformer) for ivy.
;; Usage:
;; (require 'ivy-rich)
;; (ivy-set-display-transformer 'ivy-switch-buffer 'ivy-rich-switch-buffer-transformer)
;;
